quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  71,21,"Nuuhu maaki : \"Joomi am, …ďee yeddii lam, …ďe jokkii on mo jawle mun e …ďi…ó…ďe …ďeydaali …óum si wanaa hayrugol"
  71,22,∆Āe fewji feere mawnde
  71,23,"…ďe wi'i: \"Wata on terto dey rewetee…ói mon …óin: wata on terto Wudda, e Suwaa'a, e Ya'uuqatha, e Nasr"
  71,24,"Ko pellet, …ďe majjinii ko …óuu…ói. [Joomi] wata A …ďeydir too√Īu…ďe …ďen, si wanaa majjere"
  71,25,"Ko sagu goopi ma…ď…ďe …óin …ďe yooliranoo, …ďe naadaa Yiite, …ďe he…ďanaano ko'e ma…ď…ďe faabotoo…óo gaanin Allah"
  71,26,"Nuuhu maaki kadi : \"Joomi am, wata A accu e leydi ndin, hay keefeero dilloowo"
  71,27,"Ko pellet, si A accii …ďe, …ďe majjinay jeyaa…ďe Maa …ďen, …ďe jiidoytaako si wanaa bonnoo…ďe …óuu…óu…ďe geddi"
  71,28,"Joomi am, haforanam min e jibim…ďe lam …ďen, e …ďen gom…óim…ďe naatu…ďe ka suudu am, e gom…óim…ďe wor…ďe …ďen e gom…óim…ďe rew…ďe …ďen; wata A …ďeydir too√Īu…ďe …ďen, si wanaa halakuyee"